title: Rana Mubashir Iqbal wins NA-124 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz Candidate Rana Mubashir Iqbal has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-124 Lahore-VIII by securing 55,387 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent Zamir Ahmed, who bagged 43,594 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 41.76 percent.
